Text: Noan! Can you hear me, Noan?

Name: Noan
Text: Who are you calling...?

Name: Noan
Text: The door's control terminal is... there.

Name: Noan
Text: This place is about to collapse...

Name: ...Tsk! Noan! Hurry over and help!
Text: Your "replica" has stirred up some real trouble busting in here!

Name: Noan
Text: You want the other "me" to save you?

Name: Noan
Text: ...Just one last step!

Name: Noan
Text: No more time to waste. I should just destroy it.
